       *OET do file
*By Phil Tian

clear all

set mem 250m
set maxvar 32000
set matsize 2000
set more off

capture log close
log using "OET_log", replace
use oetaug2010_pitstoplevel_v8.dta, clear

drop if psexpectation==1000
drop if psexpectation==0
gen k=ln((1-psexpectation/1000)/(psexpectation/1000))

program define OET_ML 

args lnf lngamma
tempvar m

gen double `m'=-k/exp(`lngamma')-winpc
quietly replace `lnf'=ln(normalden(ln(`m')))-ln(`m')-ln(exp(`lngamma')) if exp(`lngamma')>0 & `m'>0
quietly replace `lnf'=ln(normalden(ln(`m')))-ln(`m')-ln(-exp(`lngamma')) if exp(`lngamma')<0 & `m'>0
quietly replace `lnf'=0 if `m'<0

end

ml model lf OET_ML (lngamma:k=bet failrate winvalue sbaseline shistakes slostakes swealth red blue magenta yellow)

ml check
ml search
ml maximize
ml graph
